    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=qsvw3yb9ae]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=qsvw3yb9ae]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=a7e07epnz2]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=a7e07epnz2]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=sdcuizpyg1]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=sdcuizpyg1]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=bfx51a63m0]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=bfx51a63m0]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=pg1gx1h45y]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=pg1gx1h45y]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=o3l026tbjy]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=o3l026tbjy]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=rm3e8obqi3]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=rm3e8obqi3]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=xkgpfi7hb2]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=xkgpfi7hb2]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=nqkz659zsr]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=nqkz659zsr]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"stirling-vfx-banner.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438600/stirling-vfx-banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758104669798&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=214\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604438600/stirling-vfx-banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758104669798&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"541\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"604045354\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"stirling-vfx-banner.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604438600\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"3dacdee4-3fe0-4eee-91ab-804300ce53d2\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438600/stirling-vfx-banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758104669798&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=428 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438600/stirling-vfx-banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758104669798&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=214 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong><span data-colorid=\"a7e07epnz2\">Project</span></strong>:  Stirling VFX: </p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"nqkz659zsr\">Created &amp; Written by</span></strong>: Pierre Bournigault</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"qsvw3yb9ae\">Edited by:</span></strong> Leif Pedersen</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://downloads.renderman.pixar.com/Tutorials/Stirling_VFX/Stirling_VFX_RfM.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"DownloadButton2.png\" width=\"158\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438600/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758104625256&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604438600/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758104625256&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"604438698\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"DownloadButton2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604438600\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"f88e8290-3ab3-47f5-bada-2bcd880561c9\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438600/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758104625256&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438600/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758104625256&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37 1x\" /></span></a><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>As a 3D artist, expanding your skill set is an ongoing journey. I wanted to make the most of my free time by exploring an area I had never tackled before: live-action VFX. To challenge myself, I went outside and recorded a plate using my phone, ensuring I had to work with organic, unpredictable camera movement. </p><p>Additionally, I rented a Theta 360&deg; camera to learn how to capture my own HDRIs and integrate them into my workflow.</p><p>In this tutorial, I'll be compositing a slightly modified version of RenderMan&rsquo;s Stirling model into a parking spot. Let&rsquo;s dive in and explore this process together!</p><p /><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" allowtransparency=\"true\" class=\"fullscreen-video-iframe conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"wide\" data-local-id=\"30f03dee-7bc7-4170-9e17-da89bddd118b\" data-macro-id=\"2d74fa712adfe99fcdea80261d0d0ba1518fb8887244417da294c838377ea4eb\" data-macro-name=\"widget\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"540\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/1075783519\" style=\"border:none; margin:1em 0em;\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"960\">\n</iframe>\n\n<p /><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/657227810/Stirling+Color+Management\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657227810\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"stirling_color_thumb.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438600/stirling_color_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762588916016&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604438600/stirling_color_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762588916016&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657227910\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"stirling_color_thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604438600\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"8c3742e6-fd47-42f5-8a7a-ccdf29cb5a8f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438600/stirling_color_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762588916016&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438600/stirling_color_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762588916016&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"StirlingVFX-ColorManagement\"><span data-colorid=\"bfx51a63m0\">Color Management</span></h1><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/656998424/Stirling+Lighting\" data-linked-resource-id=\"656998424\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"stirling_hdri_thumb.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438600/stirling_hdri_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762588958660&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604438600/stirling_hdri_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762588958660&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"656998539\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"stirling_hdri_thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604438600\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"b57c7542-626b-4808-8062-ae5583cf901e\" data-media-type=\